data.description: Welcome to this stunning carriage home located in the desirable Meridian Crossing community of Bear, Delaware. At just three years old, you essentially have new construction without the wait! Only a cross country relocation allows this home for sale. This immaculate property offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a host of impressive features that are sure to captivate any discerning buyer.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and open entryway which the sellers use as the family dining area because the lighting is so amazing. This space could also be used as a sitting room or work space. Just past the dining area, you will find a dreamy kitchen, boasting granite countertops, ample storage space, and modern appliances. The open concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to the spacious living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or relaxing with family.  The hardwood floors throughout the main level add a touch of elegance to the home, while the large windows allow for an abundance of natural light to flood the rooms. The main floor laundry adds convenience to your daily routine.  Upstairs, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms, each offering a tranquil retreat after a long day. The loft area provides additional space for a home office or play area, catering to your specific needs. The master suite is a true haven, featuring a private ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet.  The large basement provides endless possibilities, offering plenty of room for storage or the potential to be finished into additional living space.  Outside, you'll find yourself in a beautiful neighborhood with well-maintained homes and a sense of community. The location of this home is highly convenient, with easy access to highways and a variety of shopping options just a short drive away.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home in Meridian Crossing your own. Schedule your private showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience that this home has to offer.
